fix what breaks 
the number we have come up with in our preliminary first cut 
at this data is 2284 hours in eva time fisher said eva for 
extravehicular activity is nasas term for space walks fisher 
said thats 32 percent higher than estimated in a similar study 
last october 
he said that would require an average of 37 space walks a week 
