might feel a bit isolated sloan said but with this system 
youre in a community inspired by environmental issues discussed 
on breadnet wheelwright students organized an essay contest and a 
cleanup project on beaver creek which runs in front of the school 
they persuaded the city council in this town of 850 people to 
proclaim april 22 as earth day 
