members fielding 174 candidates chairman jozsef antall 58 
the league of free democrats is a liberal party with 20000 
members fielding 169 candidates chairman janos kis 46 
the independent smallholders party is a rural party with 60000 
members running 165 candidates chairman vince voeroes 79 
the governing hungarian socialist party is a west europeantype 
socialist party established by reformists in the communist party 
it has 62000 members and has 170 candidates chairman rezsoe 
nyers 67 
the social democratic party of hungary is a member of the 
socialist international has 12000 members and is fielding 74 
candidates chairwoman anna petrasovits 36 
the league of young democrats is a liberal youth party that sets 
