the ussr to a certain degree according to a report prepared by 
the house task force on terrorism and unconventional warfare 
hekmatyar is definitely devoted to fighting the us and has 
cooperated with iran and other radical muslims to that end the 
paper said the task force is part of the house republican research 
committee of which mccollum is a member 
the report said hekmatyar was a member of the communist party in 
his youth and has maintained close contacts with the soviets 
hekmatyar recently joined with afghan defense minister shahnawaz 
tanai who waged an unsuccessful coup attempt march 6 against 
