galeano cornejo accused the sandinista army of repressing the 
peasants in his area in southern nicaragua he said his forces 
will not demobilize until the sandinista army does the same 
if we demobilize now we would be leaving all these peasants 
without protection galeano cornejo 22 the brother of israel 
galeano cornejo told the associated press in an interview early 
friday 
about 4000 contras are believed to be stationed in nicaragua in 
a northsouth corridor from the honduran border to costa rica 
under the accord they will move into security zones supervised by 
obando y bravo and the united nations 
