perus government with a workerpeasant state styled on the ideas 
of mao tsetung 
the rebels waged a bloody campaign of terror prior to novembers 
nationwide municipal elections killing more than 150 local 
government officials and candidates 
the government says more than 18000 people have died in the 
decade of political violence including police soldiers rebels 
government officials and civilians 
